FAQs

General Questions

What is Kaca Bazar?

Kaca Bazar is an online marketplace where farmers can sell their agricultural products directly to customers. We provide a platform to connect buyers with fresh, locally-produced goods while empowering farmers to grow their businesses.

Who can shop on Kaca Bazar?

Anyone looking to purchase high-quality agricultural products directly from farmers can shop on Kaca Bazar. Our platform is open to all customers.

Who can sell on Kaca Bazar?

Any farmer or producer who grows or makes agricultural products can sell on Kaca Bazar. It’s free to create a seller account and list your products on our platform.

For Buyers

How do I place an order?

Placing an order is simple! Browse our selection of products, add your desired items to the cart, and proceed to checkout. You’ll be able to provide your shipping details and complete your payment securely.

What payment methods are accepted?

We accept various payment methods including credit/debit cards and other secure online payment gateways. At checkout, you’ll see all available payment options.

When will I receive my order?

Delivery times vary depending on the location of the farmer and your shipping address. However, we work with our sellers to ensure timely delivery. You will receive an estimated delivery time at checkout.

Can I track my order?

Yes, once your order is confirmed and shipped, you will receive a tracking number via email so you can monitor the progress of your delivery.

What is your return policy?

Due to the nature of agricultural products, we do not accept returns. However, if there’s an issue with your order such as damaged or incorrect items, please contact our support team at support@kacabazar.com and we’ll work with the farmer to resolve the issue.

For Sellers

How do I become a seller?

Becoming a seller on Kaca Bazar is easy! Simply go to the seller registration page, fill out your details, and submit the form. Once your account is verified, you can start listing your products.

What can I sell on Kaca Bazar?

Kaca Bazar is a platform for agricultural products. This includes fruits, vegetables, grains, dairy, meat, and more. If you’re unsure whether your products qualify, feel free to reach out to us.

How do I manage my product listings?

Once you’re registered as a seller, you’ll have access to a dashboard where you can manage your product listings. You can add new products, update prices, and track your sales all from this dashboard.

How do I get paid?

After a customer makes a purchase, the payment will be securely processed and transferred to your account. Payments are typically processed within a few business days after a successful sale.

Is there any fee for selling on Kaca Bazar?

Creating a seller account and listing your products is completely free. However, Kaca Bazar takes a small commission on each sale to maintain the platform and ensure smooth transactions between buyers and sellers.

Support

How do I contact customer support?

If you need help or have any questions, you can reach out to our support team by emailing us at support@kacabazar.com. We’re here to assist you with any issues or inquiries.
